                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>London</placeName>\n                <date><add>?</add> 23. '56</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My dear friend <addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Will you inform<lb/> me, at what price you can<lb/> deliver say one\n                or two thousand<lb/> copies of your small Bible in<lb/> sheets, as binding is\n                cheaper<lb/> here than with you. I think<lb/> your prospectus <add>?</add> $1â€”<lb/>\n                I believe they could be used<lb/> here at about 5. shillings to<lb/> 5 shillings\n                &amp; sixpence English<lb/> currency, &amp; the Exchange being <lb/>in your favor\n                &amp; the freight<lb/> by sailing vessels not heavy<lb/> &amp; are in hopes of\n                getting you<lb/> an order. Your agent here<lb/> has sold out what you sent<lb/> but\n                the price is considered<lb/> exhorbitant. Let me hear<lb/> fully from you in this\n                &amp;</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3tm72m5m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
