                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>any collateral <add>?</add> at, and<lb/> write me in such manner<lb/> as to enable me\n                to hand<lb/> your letter to some gentlemen<lb/> here who may thereupon<lb/> send you\n                an order. Of course<lb/> you will save all commissions<lb/> in filling any order\n                emanating<lb/> through one and this, should<lb/> become a part of your<lb/>\n                calculation. I thank you<lb/> for the Occident sent. If I<lb/> can serve you I\n                shall<lb/> do it, I have only seen<lb/>\n                <persName>Dr. Adler</persName> for a short time<lb/> as my time is full\n                occupied<lb/> Wishing you health and<lb/> peace of mind I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">as ever yours very truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">G Kursheedt</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written upside down at the bottom of the page\">I see the\n                Occident comes to <persName><add>?</add> Moses</persName><lb/> so you need not send\n                me more</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3tm72m5m/canvas/p2"
